  "purpose": "Define role-based Academy learning routes, onboarding, self-training, training requests and commercial education requirements without changing frontend runtime.",
  "principles": [
    "Academy is a strategic module, not a superficial help page.",
    "Every role must understand what the platform does, how to operate it, why it saves time and what value it adds.",
    "Training must be role-based and module-aware.",
    "The platform should reduce the need for long manual onboarding, while still allowing users to request live training by topic.",
    "Academy content must support internal operations, shoppers, consultants/franchisees/partners and final clients.",
    "Academy must also support commercial education and cross-sell of additional modules, services, integrations and packages."
  ],
